Do not output any additional explanation, markdown formatting, bullets, or prose after the subject line.
Do not wrap the document or the subject in code fences in your final text.
Do not ask the user for confirmation or write "Would you like me to..." questions.
Submit the artifact now, not as a proposal for later approval.
Call the tool before emitting any final text. If you skip the tool call, the task has failed.
